Some suggestions for you adventurers 1.The game may have few players when it is just launched, we recommend you to find your teammates in the community in advance. 2.Early access does not mean the final quality, we will gradually improve 3.Please be civilized in multiplayer games and do not involve in sensitive topics such as politics. WHAT IS NOTME? Not me is an asymmetric VR game. The theme is an exciting survival adventure on a deserted island, as a werewolf or human. Eight adventurers will explore the mysterious island, but the ship has been damaged by the storm. The werewolves on the island had already killed the two adventurers and blended into the team. You must discover who the wolves are while trying to gather supplies and repair the boat. If you have more questions, please join our discord and contact the administrator
